content:
Maintain Your Contact Center

Keep your contact center running optimally. Use the latest version of contact center components and, as needed, delete customers’ personal identifiable information (PII) from your Service Cloud Voice contact center.

Manage Your Contact Center in Amazon Connect: Quickly access the Amazon Connect settings page for your contact center. 

Delete Voice Call Customer Data: Delete customers’ personal identifiable information (PII) from your Service Cloud Voice contact center.
title: Maintaining Contact Centers with Service Cloud
